# Cloudflare Web Analytics beacon token (cookieless analytics, NFR-11).
# Create a site under Cloudflare dashboard -> Analytics & Logs -> Web Analytics,
# copy the token from its JS snippet, and set it here (or in the Cloudflare Pages
# build environment variables). When unset, no beacon is emitted.
#
# Do NOT also enable dashboard auto-injection on Cloudflare Pages while this is
# set — it would count every page view twice.
PUBLIC_CF_BEACON_TOKEN=
